c.detail:
Thunderstone Mine: DC 15 to find, DC 15 to disable;
    affects all targets within 20 ft., DC 13 save or take 2d10 thunder damage
    and become deafened for 1d4 rounds

south.trap:
Acid Spray: DC 10 to find, DC 15 to disable;
    affects all targets within a 20 ft. cone, DC 13 save or take 1d10 acid damage
    for 1d4 rounds
